n_start --> mg_enter : Wade into the mangrove coast.
n_start --> cf_enter : Climb toward the cloud-forest ridge.
n_start --> cv_enter : Descend into the sink-hole caverns.
n_start --> tw_enter : Cross to the ruined survey tower.
n_start --> tf_enter : Walk out onto the tidal flats.
mg_enter --> mg_bridge : Follow the log bridge upcoast.
mg_enter --> mg_oyster : Pick along the oyster rocks downcoast.
mg_enter --> mg_creek : Push inland up the hidden creek.
mg_enter --> mg_lagoon : Wade toward the still green lagoon.
mg_bridge --> mg_carve : Stop to copy the carved driftwood.
mg_bridge --> mg_farbank : Hurry across before the tide.
mg_carve --> mg_highground : Trust the arrow toward high ground.
mg_carve --> mg_readmarks : Read the marks slowly for a message.
mg_readmarks --> mg_highground : Head for high ground as Alder marked.
mg_farbank --> e_mg_mud_trap : Cross the mud slick quickly.
mg_farbank --> mg_highground : Keep to the firm palms.
mg_highground --> L_cove : Take the goat track down to the cove.
mg_highground --> mg_seep : Angle inland toward a spring gully.
mg_oyster --> mg_turtle_note : Study the turtle and read the tide pools...
mg_oyster --> mg_rockpath : Search the rocks for a way inland.
mg_turtle_note --> mg_rockpath : Mark the turtle and press on inland.
mg_turtle_note --> e_mg_turtle_seen : Stop and right the turtle now.
mg_rockpath --> mg_seep : Follow the clear seep upward.
mg_seep --> L_fresh : Climb to the bright spring pool.
mg_seep --> mg_overhang : Duck under the mossy overhang.
mg_overhang --> cove_rise : Follow Alder's arrow toward the camp.
mg_overhang --> e_mg_shelter : Copy the firepit shelter and rest a whil...
mg_creek --> mg_otter : Follow the otters upstream.
mg_creek --> mg_trees : Cut away from the water into the trees.
mg_creek --> mg_heron : Pole across to the loud heron island.
mg_otter --> mg_seep : Climb along the sweet water.
mg_trees --> mg_highground : Climb toward the brightness.
mg_trees --> mg_gametrail : Take the level game trail.
mg_gametrail --> mg_highground : Backtrack toward the bright rise.
mg_gametrail --> e_mg_lost : Gamble on one more bend.
cf_enter --> cf_switch : Take the steep switchback up.
cf_enter --> cf_traverse : Angle across the gentle traverse.
cf_enter --> cf_hollow : Drop to the pale gleam in the hollow.
cf_enter --> cf_falls : Follow the roar toward a hidden waterfal...
cf_switch --> cf_ledge : Climb the bare rock rib.
cf_switch --> cf_shelf : Follow the green shelf.
cf_ledge --> cf_bench : Follow the ridge path higher.
cf_shelf --> cf_bench : Join the ridge path.
cf_bench --> cf_campapproach : Climb the stony trail toward the camp.
cf_bench --> cf_grove : Detour into the grove of ancient trees.
cf_campapproach --> camp_ascent1 : Follow the cairns onto the high ridge.
camp_ascent1 --> camp_ascent2 : Push on along the cairned ridge.
camp_ascent2 --> camp_ascent3a : Take the sheltered ledge.
camp_ascent2 --> camp_ascent3b : Brave the airy crest.
camp_ascent2 --> e_ascent_daunted : Stop here, daunted by the height.
camp_ascent3a --> camp_ascent4 : Rejoin the ridgeline.
camp_ascent3b --> camp_ascent4 : Come down to the level shelf.
camp_ascent4 --> camp_ascent5 : Make the final pull to the camp.
camp_ascent5 --> L_camp : Step into Alder's camp.
cf_traverse --> L_fresh : Rest at the spring.
cf_traverse --> cf_upper : Keep traversing along the slope.
cf_traverse --> cf_dell : Follow a deer path to a hidden dell.
cf_upper --> cf_bench : Climb the faint path on.
cf_upper --> cf_hollow : Drop to the pale gleam.
